#. type: Title =
#: ../src/dashboard.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "控制台界面"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/dashboard.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The dashboard UI appears when you interact with a factory controller block. "
"It displays a virtual 2D board on which you can place xref:factory-"
"gauge.adoc[factory gauges] (and xref:components.adoc[other components])."
msgstr ""
"与工厂控制台方块交互即可打开控制台界面。控制台界面可用于放置xref:factory-"
"gauge.adoc[工厂仪表]（及xref:components.adoc[其他组件]）。"

